sentences: Chittaranjan Tripathy (born 1971) is an Odia director, music director and actor.
He completed his MA in Sociology at the University of Hyderabad and, in 1996, a Diploma in Acting at the National School of Drama in Delhi.
In 2007, Tripathy came to the Odia movie industry with his film Dhauli Express, for which he was producer, director, scriptwriter, music director, lyricist and playback singer.
He made another movie Mukhyamantri in 2009.
He also played the negative character in the latest ALT Balaji and ZEE5 web-series M.O. M Mission Over Mars (2019).
2007 - Mohana Sundara Dev Goswami Award - Dhauli Express
2007 - Odisha State Film Award for Best Music Director - Dhauli Express
2007 - Odisha State Film Award for Best Singer - Dhauli Express
2016 - Odisha State Film Award for Best Comedian - Love you Jessica
